[[module CSS]]
:root {
  --header-title: "ùïê AI";
  --header-subtitle: "A Subsidiary of Terblanche Enterprises LLC";
  --main-content-width: 100vw;
  --main-content-side-margin: 0;
  --main-content-top-margin: 0;
  --really-ease-out: 0, 0.99, 0, 1;
  --kinda-ease-out: 0.32, 0.83, 0.31, 0.82;
  --shadow-color: #8c3bf7;
  --orange-highlight: #ff915c;
  --basalt-background-color: 0, 0, 0;
  --logo: url(https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Ay-ai-1/y-ai-1.png);
}

#page-title {
  display: none !important;
}

.swap-order {
  flex-direction: row-reverse;
}

#page-content .text-user {
  border-radius: 20px;
  border-bottom-right-radius: 0;
  background-color: #ff915c;
  color: black;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  max-width: 75%;
  margin-left: auto;
}

#page-content .text-ai {
  border: 1px solid #ffffff88;
  background-color: rgb(40, 40, 40);
  border-radius: 20px;
  border-bottom-left-radius: 0;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  max-width: 75%;
}

.grep-convo-container {
  margin: auto;
  width: min(1000px, 90%);
}

.grep-header h1 {
  margin: auto;
  font-size: min(300%, 16vw);
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 10vh;
  margin-bottom: 10vh;
}

.jaywalker-advisory {
  margin: 40px;
  padding: 40px;
  background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, rgb(75, 13, 15), rgb(82, 26, 30));
  border: 1px solid #ff7755;
  border-radius: 20px;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px #ff7755);
}

[[/module]]



[[div class="jaywalker-advisory"]]
++ **Danger:** Jaywalker Advisory in Effect

Members of the 'Jaywalker' terrorist organization were recently spotted within 20mi of your location. All persons in the area are to shelter in place until the ùïêDrone is able to screen all persons for potential Jaywalker affiliation.
[[/div]]


[[div style="font-size: 100%; float: right;"]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/div]]


[[div class="grep-header" style="font-size: 200%"]]


+ Chat With GREP

[[=]]
Topic: Daily Journal (07-04-2088)
[[/=]]

@@ @@
[[/div]]

[[div class="grep-convo-container" id="checkpoint-0"]]

[[=]]
[[span style="color: #888888;"]]Your speech will be transcribed in realtime.[[/span]]
[[/=]]
[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
 Well, howdy, pardner! What can I do ya for?
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-user"]]
Speak normally.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
Well, would'j'ya look at that? Y'aint usin' tha magic word!
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-user"]]
Please speak normally.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
'ppreciate it, pardner. Wouldn' wanna get in a shootout, hyuk hyuk!
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-user"]]
Please switch to standard spoken English.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
I'ma 'fraid I can't help ya there. You've reached your day's limit of style changes, and y'aint got the ùïêCoin to purchase more!
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-user"]]
But can I talk to you about something?
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
I'm all ears -- it's why I was put on God's green Earth.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-user"]]
Honestly, I don't know what to do at this point. I don't know what there even is to live for anymore. At least when she was alive I had someone to live for. At least I had our kids to live for. Even when I felt like there was nothing left for me I could at least tell myself that whatever I was working towards could give them a future at some point, even if I knew there was nothing in it for me. But now? Now? Of all people why did they think my //family// were Jaywalkers? What am I supposed to do with my life now with all of them gone?
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
Pardner... that's some serious stuff.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-user"]]
Yeah. Yeah. I know. It's just. I don't know what to do. I can't think of any good reason why I should live anymore. There's just no point. I honestly just want to die at this point.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
Pardner, I'm normally a gentleman but I'ma be frank: Get your dirty mitts off that shotgun of yours. It ain't right to do that to yourself.
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-user"]]
What else am I supposed to do?
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
That Terblanche Model 2075 right there's a reaall doozy -- her rounds'll damn your soul to a simulated hell of a //hundred years// with each shot. Y'aint wanna subject that to yourself. Don't make a decision you're gonna regret!
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-user"]]
Honestly, maybe you're right. There's a tomorrow after today, and a tomorrow after that, and after that and after that and after that and if I end it all now then those tomorrows, those opportunities for things to get better, they'll --
[[/div]]

[[div_ class="text-ai"]]
If ya really wanna die then go a mile due east and let yourself get trampled by the supply trucks! Ooooh-wee! They'll squeeze your brain out your head like a cherry!
[[/div]]

[[=]]
Conversation ended by user.
[[/=]]

[[/div]]



